Package com.iontrading.mkv.qos

Class MkvConnectionQoS

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iontrading.mkv.qos.MkvConnectionQoS
  • @Keep
@KeepPublicClassMemberNames
public class MkvConnectionQoS
extends Object
    A configuration class for connections.

    This class contains a set of properties which can be passed for customizing connections requested via the createClient method.
    Some properties overrides global ones. Others are Java specific and can be setted only using this class.

    See Also:
    MkvPlatform
